Package: astrozorpub
Type: Package
Title: Publish Quarto / RMarkdown Documents to Astrozor
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Astrozor", "Project", email = "noreply@astrozor.cz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    RStudio addin and helper functions for publishing rendered Quarto or
    RMarkdown documents (HTML output + assets) to an Astrozor instance.
    Bundles the rendered HTML directory into a ZIP and POSTs it to the
    site's /publish/quarto endpoint using a personal access token stored
    in .Renviron as ASTROZOR_TOKEN.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite,
    fs,
    cli,
    miniUI,
    shiny,
    rstudioapi,
    zip
Suggests:
    quarto,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
